  "subject": "Refactoring DMaaP config reading",
  "commit_message": "Refactoring DMaaP config reading\n\n- Introducing new DMaaPChannel/DMaaPChannels classes\n to hold DMaaP channel configuration\n- There are two ways to read config:\n\t> List of DMaaPChannel can be parsed directly from\n\tlegacy-formatted JSON file using Jackson\n\t> DMaaPChannel instances can be created with info parsed\n\tusing Regex from URLs found in config file following new format\n- Removing previously used HashMap and introducing new one\nthat allows retrieving DMaaPChannel objects from their name\n- Refactoring EventPublisher to use DMaaPChannel instance\nobtained from DMaapPropertyReader channel map\n- Rewriting DmaapPropertyReader unit test to use DMaaPChannel\nand including tests for new config format\n\nIssue-Id: DCAEGEN2-129\nChange-Id: I34c9014b597580fa03bb69e3234ef5dfe0d046e6\nSigned-off-by: Konstantinos Kanonakis <konstantinos.kanonakis@huawei.com>\n",
